Visitors play virtual reality games at the Global Mobile Internet Conference (GMIC), which opened in Guangzhou, South China's Guangdong Province on July 26. The GMIC Guangzhou 2019 shows how the latest developments in science and technology like 5G and artificial intelligence are being integrated into daily life through film, music and fashion. Photo: IC  
